               <p>
                  <rs id="t17871024-54-verdict284" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17871024-54-verdict284" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17871024-54-verdict284" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY, Of stealing to the value of 5 s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17871024-54-punish285" type="punishmentDescription">
