                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871024-54-defend472 t17871024-54-punish285"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>MARY M'CARTY, <rs id="t17871024-54-verdict286" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17871024-54-verdict286" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
